sequenceDiagram
    participant BROWSER as Browser
    participant PROXY as Next.js Proxy<br/>(next.config.ts)
    participant FASTAPI as FastAPI Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant WORKER as AnalysisWorker
    participant GITHUB as GitHub API
    participant CHROMA as ChromaDB
    participant OLLAMA as Ollama LLM

    Note over BROWSER,PROXY: ⚠️ Login bypasses proxy via hard-coded URL

    BROWSER->>FASTAPI: GET /api/auth/github/login (direct)
    FASTAPI->>GITHUB: OAuth redirect
    GITHUB-->>FASTAPI: GET /api/auth/github/callback?code=...
    FASTAPI->>GITHUB: POST /login/oauth/access_token
    FASTAPI->>GITHUB: GET /user
    FASTAPI->>DB: get_or_create_user()
    FASTAPI-->>BROWSER: Set-Cookie: access_token=JWT; redirect to frontend

    BROWSER->>PROXY: GET /api/repos (Cookie: access_token)
    PROXY->>FASTAPI: GET /api/repos (forwarded with cookie)
    FASTAPI->>DB: jwt.decode + User query (get_current_user)
    FASTAPI->>DB: Repository + Analysis + Artifact queries
    FASTAPI-->>PROXY: {"repositories": [...]}
    PROXY-->>BROWSER: JSON response

    BROWSER->>PROXY: POST /api/import {"url": "..."}
    PROXY->>FASTAPI: POST /api/import
    FASTAPI->>GITHUB: check_repo_limits()
    FASTAPI->>DB: Create Repository, Analysis, AnalysisJob
    FASTAPI-->>BROWSER: {"status": "Queued"}

    Note over FASTAPI,WORKER: Background job processing

    FASTAPI->>WORKER: enqueue(job_id)
    WORKER->>GITHUB: download_repo_zipball() → /tmp/
    WORKER->>WORKER: AnalysisEngine.run() (AST parsing + analysis)
    WORKER->>DB: Save AnalysisArtifact(core_model, blob_data)
    WORKER->>DB: analysis.status = "Completed"

    BROWSER->>PROXY: GET /api/repos/{name}/scan (polling every 3s)
    PROXY->>FASTAPI: GET /api/repos/{name}/scan
    FASTAPI->>DB: get_or_build_model() → deserialize JSON
    FASTAPI-->>BROWSER: {"status": "completed", "hierarchy": {...}}

    BROWSER->>PROXY: EventSource /api/repos/{name}/tasks/stream
    PROXY->>FASTAPI: GET /api/repos/{name}/tasks/stream (SSE)
    Note over FASTAPI: Keeps connection open, sends events

    BROWSER->>PROXY: POST /api/repos/{name}/semantic-index
    PROXY->>FASTAPI: POST
    FASTAPI->>CHROMA: create_collection + add embeddings (background)
    FASTAPI-->>BROWSER: {"status": "processing"}
    FASTAPI-->>BROWSER: SSE: {"semantic_index": "completed"}

    BROWSER->>PROXY: GET /api/repos/{name}/semantic-search?q=auth
    PROXY->>FASTAPI: GET
    FASTAPI->>CHROMA: collection.query(["auth"])
    FASTAPI->>DB: get_or_build_model()
    FASTAPI-->>BROWSER: {"results": [...]}

    BROWSER->>PROXY: POST /api/repos/{name}/summary/generate
    PROXY->>FASTAPI: POST
    FASTAPI->>OLLAMA: POST /api/generate (background)
    OLLAMA-->>FASTAPI: Generated markdown
    FASTAPI->>DB: Save AnalysisArtifact(summary)
    FASTAPI-->>BROWSER: SSE: {"summary": "completed"}
